OL,3,C62% of Guernsey's poorest homes do not
OL,4,Chave enough beds, report finds
OL,6,FNearly two thirds of Guernsey's
OL,7,Fpoorest say they do not have enough
OL,8,Fbeds for each person in their
OL,9,Fhousehold, according to the first ever
OL,10,Freport into quality of life in the
OL,11,Fisland.
OL,13,FThe Guernsey Community Foundation's
OL,14,Freport includes data from one of the
OL,15,Flargest surveys ever conducted locally
OL,16,Fwith 3,000 islanders taking part.
OL,18,FIts first ever publication aims to
OL,19,Fshine a light on the gap in life
OL,20,Fquality between the island's
OL,21,Fwealthiest and poorest people.
