OL,3,C62% of Guernsey's poorest homes do not
OL,4,Chave enough beds, report finds
OL,6,FOne islander we spoke to says it is
OL,7,Foften hard to afford the basics for
OL,8,Fher and her two children.
OL,10,FAlly De Carteret said: "I always try
OL,11,Fto do my best to make sure the
OL,12,Fchildren are clothed, have been fed,
OL,13,Fhave electric, heating, which means
OL,14,Fthat sometimes I don't necessarily get
OL,15,Fto do X, Y and Z or sometimes I will
OL,16,Fgo without having certain meals I want
OL,17,Fto make sure that my kids have eaten
OL,18,Fand that's that."
