OL,3,C62% of Guernsey's poorest homes do not
OL,4,Chave enough beds, report finds
OL,6,FSpeaking on the report's findings, Jim
OL,7,FRoberts, chief executive of the
OL,8,FGuernsey Community Foundation told ITV
OL,9,FNews: "If you look at the life lived
OL,10,Fby low income households in Guernsey,
OL,11,Fit's in stark contrast to the life
OL,12,Fenjoyed by wealthier households.
OL,14,F"Now, some people would say that's
OL,15,Fobvious, but what I hope the report
OL,16,Fdoes is unpack what that means in
OL,17,Freality.
