OL,6,F"So it is things like not having
OL,7,Fenough beds, not having carpets or
OL,8,Fflooring, putting off going to the
OL,9,Fdoctor, becoming increasingly socially
OL,10,Fisolated."
OL,12,FJim added: "I think in terms of a call
OL,13,Fto action or a reminder of the work
OL,14,Fthat needs to be done in the social
OL,15,Fwelfare sphere, then this report is
OL,16,Funparalleled."
