OL,4,Chave enough beds, report finds
OL,6,FJim also says that while the report
OL,7,Foffers no recommendations for what
OL,8,Faction needs to be taken by the
OL,9,Fgovernment, he hopes candidates
OL,10,Fstanding at next month's election will
OL,11,Fuse the report's findings to inform
OL,12,Ftheir stances on a range of topics
OL,13,Frelating to how islanders are living
OL,14,Fon a day-to-day basis.
OL,16,FHe added: "One of the motivations for
OL,17,Fproducing the report is that
OL,18,Fgovernment periodically puts out its
OL,19,Fown statistics but there's very often
OL,20,Fno narrative around that or no story
OL,21,Fbeing told.
