OL,6,FGuernsey's suicide rate has also
OL,7,Fdoubled since 2015, which the report
OL,8,Fsays should 'cause concern',
OL,9,Fespecially given suicide figures
OL,10,Fremain significantly higher than those
OL,11,Fin neighbouring Jersey.
OL,13,FWhen asked about rising suicides in
OL,14,Fthe island, Alex Lemon from the
OL,15,Ffoundation, said: "I think it's
OL,16,Fincredibly serious.
OL,18,F"There are some real underlying
OL,19,Fproblems that are not well understood
OL,20,Fbecause we don't understand why the
OL,21,Fnumbers are so different.
